def get_noise(n_samples, z_dim,isFlatten = True):
    
    nz_dim = None
    
    if isFlatten:
        nz_dim = 1
        for i in range(len(z_dim)):
            nz_dim *= z_dim[i]
    else:        
        nz_dim = z_dim

    return np.random.uniform(-1.,1.,(n_samples,*nz_dim)).astype(np.float32)
In [3]:
def resizeImages(imgs, size = (64,64)):
    
    new = np.zeros((imgs.shape[0],*size),dtype=np.float32)
    
    for i in range(imgs.shape[0]):
        new[i] = cv2.resize(imgs[i],size)
        
    return np.expand_dims(new,-1)

mnist_imgs = mnist.train.images
mnist_imgs = np.reshape(mnist_imgs,(mnist_imgs.shape[0],28,28))
new_mnist = resizeImages(mnist_imgs)

def showImage(image_tensor, num_images=10, size=(1, 28, 28)):
    
    print(image_tensor.shape)
    
    image_tensor = np.reshape(image_tensor,(image_tensor.shape[0],size[1],size[2]))
    
    for i in range(num_images):
        
        plt.imshow(image_tensor[i])
        plt.show()

class Generator:
    
    def __init__(self,in_size,hid_size,out_size,isFlatten = True):
        
        self.in_size = in_size
        self.hid_size = hid_size
        
        
        if isFlatten:
            self.out_size = 1
            for i in range(len(out_size)):
                self.out_size *= out_size[i]
        else:        
            self.out_size = out_size

            
    def forward(self,inp,reuse = False):
        
        with tf.variable_scope("GAN/Generator",reuse=reuse):
            
            
            conv1 = tf.layers.conv2d_transpose(inp,self.hid_size*8,4,1,activation=tf.nn.relu)
            b1 = tf.layers.batch_normalization(conv1)
            
            conv2 = tf.layers.conv2d_transpose(b1,self.hid_size*4,4,2,"same",activation=tf.nn.relu)
            b2 = tf.layers.batch_normalization(conv2)
            
            conv3 = tf.layers.conv2d_transpose(b2,self.hid_size*2,4,2,"same",activation=tf.nn.relu)
            b3 = tf.layers.batch_normalization(conv3)
            
            conv4 = tf.layers.conv2d_transpose(b3,self.hid_size,4,2,"same",activation=tf.nn.relu)
            b4 = tf.layers.batch_normalization(conv4)
            
            out = tf.layers.conv2d_transpose(b4,1,4,2,"same")
            
        
        return out

class Discriminator:
    
    def __init__(self,in_size,hid_size,out_size,isFlatten = True):
        
        self.hid_size = hid_size
        self.out_size = out_size
        
        if isFlatten:
            self.in_size = 1
            for i in range(len(in_size)):
                self.in_size *= in_size[i]
        else:        
            self.in_size = in_size

            
    def forward(self,inp,reuse = False):
        
        with tf.variable_scope("GAN/Discriminator",reuse=reuse):
            
            
            conv1 = tf.layers.conv2d(inp,self.hid_size,4,2,"same",activation=tf.nn.leaky_relu)
            
            conv2 = tf.layers.conv2d(conv1,self.hid_size*2,4,2,"same",activation=tf.nn.leaky_relu)
            b1 = tf.layers.batch_normalization(conv2)
            
            conv3 = tf.layers.conv2d(b1,self.hid_size*4,4,2,"same",activation=tf.nn.leaky_relu)
            b2 = tf.layers.batch_normalization(conv3)
            
            conv4 = tf.layers.conv2d(b2,self.hid_size*8,4,2,"same",activation=tf.nn.leaky_relu)
            b3 = tf.layers.batch_normalization(conv4)
            
            
            out = tf.layers.dense(tf.layers.flatten(tf.layers.conv2d(b3,1,4,1)),1)
        
        return out
In [8]:
def discLoss(fake_preds,real_preds):
    
    
    disc_real_pred = real_preds
    disc_real_loss = tf.nn.sigmoid_cross_entropy_with_logits(logits = disc_real_pred, labels = tf.ones_like(disc_real_pred))
    
    disc_fake_pred = fake_preds
    disc_fake_loss = tf.nn.sigmoid_cross_entropy_with_logits(logits = disc_fake_pred, labels = tf.zeros_like(disc_fake_pred))
    
    disc_loss = tf.reduce_mean(disc_fake_loss + disc_real_loss)

    return disc_loss
In [9]:
def genLoss(fake_preds):
    
    disc_fake_pred = fake_preds
    gen_loss = tf.nn.sigmoid_cross_entropy_with_logits(logits = disc_fake_pred, labels = tf.ones_like(disc_fake_pred))
    
    return tf.reduce_mean(gen_loss)

def train(img_size,disc,gen,lr = 0.001,n_epochs = 10):
    
    num_batches = 250
    noise_dim = (1,1,100)
    real_dim = img_size
    
    noiseData = get_noise(new_mnist.shape[0],noise_dim,False)

    
    with tf.Session() as sess:

    
        X = tf.placeholder(tf.float32,[None,*real_dim])
        Z = tf.placeholder(tf.float32,[None,*noise_dim])
        
        fake_imgs = gen.forward(Z)
                
        real_preds = disc.forward(X)
        fake_preds = disc.forward(fake_imgs,reuse=True)    
        
    
        disc_loss = discLoss(fake_preds,real_preds)
        gen_loss = genLoss(fake_preds)

        gen_vars = tf.get_collection(tf.GraphKeys.GLOBAL_VARIABLES,scope="GAN/Generator")
        disc_vars = tf.get_collection(tf.GraphKeys.GLOBAL_VARIABLES,scope="GAN/Discriminator")

        gen_step = tf.train.AdamOptimizer(learning_rate=lr).minimize(gen_loss,var_list = gen_vars) # G Train step
        disc_step = tf.train.AdamOptimizer(learning_rate=lr).minimize(disc_loss,var_list = disc_vars) # D Train step

                
        init = tf.global_variables_initializer()
        sess.run(init)
        
        for i in range(n_epochs):
            
            for j in range(int(mnist.train.images.shape[0]/num_batches)-1):
            
                X_batch = new_mnist[num_batches*j:num_batches*(j+1),:]
                Z_batch = noiseData[num_batches*j:num_batches*(j+1),:]

                _, dloss = sess.run([disc_step, disc_loss], feed_dict={X: X_batch, Z: Z_batch})

                _, gloss = sess.run([gen_step, gen_loss], feed_dict={Z: Z_batch})
                
                if j%100 == 0:
                    print (f"steps: {j} Discriminator loss: {dloss} Generator loss: {gloss}")
        
                
            print("Fake images : ")
            showImage(gen.forward(Z_batch,True).eval(feed_dict={Z: Z_batch}),size=(1,64,64))
                
            print("Real images : ")
            showImage(image_tensor=X_batch,size=(1,64,64))
                
            print(dloss.shape,gloss.shape)
            print (f"Epochs: {i} Discriminator loss: {dloss} Generator loss: {gloss}")
